{"tid":2429893,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"怎樣才算針死人","createTime":"2021-03-02T14:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T12:13:13.000Z","uid":234509,"like":120,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"40e1821e5051dfd33a4746d274b67f6214d2bc6f","tid":2429893,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:59:54.000Z","msg":"1.有食早餐<br />\n2.不能長期病患<br />\n3. 打針當日天氣必須良好<br />\n4.你不能把疫苗注射在接種人體內<br />\n5.打針護士必須有三十年以上經驗<br />\n6.你不能反政府<br />\n7.你不能在過往接種任何疫苗<br />\n8.接種後不能進食，否則會被視為食物中毒<br />\n9.接種後不能扑野，否則會被視為馬上風<br />\n10.接種後不能做運動，否則會被視為體力不支而死<br />\n11. 接種者必須為壯年<br />\n12. 接種者收入不能低於貧窮線 否則會被視為呃賠償<br />\n13. 接種者必須為中國人<br />\n14. 接種者必須身體健壯<br />\n15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心死了，政府也會說你是打疫苗搞到死，說你是呃賠償，說你無恥。政府總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不是打疫苗而死。"},{"pid":"e20609edc8585b522923f7ffb8701c849e8cc58a","tid":2429893,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e44f02027706219011e79d94d64fbaea3c7ac88","tid":2429893,"uid":387461,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">16.政府保留最終決定權</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"74ca017f922f044dd47cbd4032e52e7fae263d52","tid":2429893,"uid":73381,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:03:48.000Z","msg":"打針當日天氣必須良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391a7639a03dac667d5be3ac360e614b37233476","tid":2429893,"uid":127177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T15:04:28.000Z","msg":"推屋企廢老去打，賠幾球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c459934cc